uk.ac.ox.krr.logmap2.mappings

Class MappingManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ox.krr.logmap2.mappings.MappingManager
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CandidateMappingManager

    public abstract class MappingManager
extends java.lang.Object
    This class defines the basic methods to provide the anchors between two ontologies Mappings have been used to index mappings and their direction then the entry ide_a:{id_b, id_bb} will represent the mappings ide_a->ide_b and ide_a->ide_bb (with the exception of structures representing equivalence mappings.)
    Author:
    ernesto
